::Starlight/Fenox::

Starlight stumbles back as Fenox's shot hits her in the shoulder. She 
and Fenox both look back at Windlord.

"Allright, Maximal, don't move," Starlight says, taking out a charge 
and holding it over Teltoli's body, "Or this femm isn't going to live 
through this."

Behind Windlord, Fenox aims a rifle at him.
